# Global ~/.gitignore_global on macOS may carry an `Icon?` rule (Finder's
# Icon\r metadata file). On case-insensitive filesystems it incidentally
# matches both the `icons` directory and real PWA icon files like
# icon-192.png. Explicit negations below keep the manifest-referenced
# icons tracked regardless of the user's global ignore config.
!apps/web/public/icons/
!apps/web/public/icons/*.png

